data.description: This 1.1 acre of open waterfront property sits on a wide part of Rabbit Creek. Down a private drive w/ ample room for parking recreational vehicles, you’ll find this property perfect for boating, fishing & relaxion. The private dock features covered boat parking, 2 boat lifts & a jet ski lift. Newly built deck has aluminum railings & hot tub power hookup. A grand staircase, overlooking the water, leads down to a sandy area. Inside, a remodeled kitchen (+/- 6 yrs) features painted cabinets, stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar, & reverse osmosis water filtration system. Dining area flows into an open-concept living space, w/ an electric fireplace w/ Opti-Mist insert, custom mantle, & built-ins. The downstairs master suite also has a view of the water and an exit out to the deck. The ensuite bathroom features a jacuzzi tub, double vanity, & walk-in tile shower. A walk-through closet connects to the laundry area. The downstair level is finished out w 1/2 bath, & a room that can be used as a movie room, exercise space, or bonus area, w/ access to the 2-car garage. Upstairs loft area can serve as an office or extra living space. All upstairs new Luxury Vinyl Plank (LVP) flooring has been installed. 2 more bedrooms have walk-in closets, & a full bathroom connects to one bedroom & the hall. Most windows in the house have been replaced for energy efficiency. In 2021, the downstairs HVAC was replaced, & a dehumidifier was added to the upstairs unit. The metal roof is approx. 8 years old. Recent care includes septic tank field line replacement 2020, serviced & pumped in Sept 2023. A transferrable retreatment termite bond w/ E3 pest control is valid until Sept 2024; flood policy w/ Allstate is also transferable. This home is eligible for a loan assumption at a 2.5% Interest Rate. Current loan is VA, but Buyer does not have to be a Veteran to qualify. Closing to be in approx. 60 days.  This waterfront property is sold as-is, providing you with a clean slate to personalize and make it your own.    (ANY/ALL UPDATES ARE PER SELLER).  LISTING BROKER MAKES NO REPRESENTATION TO SQUARE FOOTAGE ACCURACY. BUYER TO VERIFY.
